HEADWORD: Modus vivendi
<hw>Mo"dus vi*ven"di</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L.]</ety> <def>Mode,
or manner, of living; hence, a temporary arrangement of affairs until
disputed matters can be settled.</def>⟦br⟧
